+----+-------------+--------+------------+------+-----------------+-----------------+---------+-------+------+----------+-------------+
|  1 | SIMPLE      | t_user | NULL       | ref  | user_name_index | user_name_index | 1023    | const |    1 |   100.00 | Using index |
+----+-------------+--------+------------+------+-----------------+-----------------+---------+-------+------+----------+-------------+
1 row in set, 1 warning (0.00 sec)
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

